PigeonAscent Portmaster Release (https://github.com/christianhaitian/PortMaster) 
=========================

Original version by:
	https://github.com/Escada-Games/pigeonAscent

Portmaster Version: 	

- tekkenfede https://github.com/Tekkenfede/PortMaster
	
Special thanks to: Kloptops for suggesting some fix and the PortMaster team for helping me test it! To conclude, a special thanks at Cebion for making me discover this game and obviusly for porting the frt runtime.

To compile:
===========

wget https://downloads.tuxfamily.org/godotengine/3.5.2/godot-3.5.2-stable.tar.xz
tar xf godot-3.5.2-stable.tar.xz
cd godot-3.5.2-stable/platform
git clone https://github.com/Cebion/frt.git
cd ../
scons platform=frt tools=no target=release use_llvm=yes module_webm_enabled=no -j12
strip bin/godot.frt.opt.llvm

Instructions:
=============

To run the game start pigeon.sh from your ports folder.


Controls:
=============

A/Y			= Mouse Click/Accept
B/R Analog Down	        = Scroll Down
X/R Analog Up		= Scroll Up
DPAD/L Analog	    = Move Cursor